          <h1 className="text-sm font-bold tracking-tight text-[#F7E7CE] serif leading-none uppercase">Aneela's</h1>
          <span className="text-[8px] text-[#F7E7CE]/60 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-medium">Professional Artistry</span>
